'''蟄龍介目'''（学名：{{lang|la|'''Terebellida'''}}）是[[环节动物门|环节动物门]][[多毛纲|多毛纲]]下的一个[[目_(生物)|目]]，目前轄下有13個科<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.marinespecies.org/polychaeta/ |title=The World Polychaeta Database |accessdate=2016-08-24 |editor1=Read, G. |editor2=[[克里斯蒂安·法乌查尔德|Fauchald, K.]] |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108123959/http://www.marinespecies.org/polychaeta/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，可以再細分成兩個亞目<ref name="WoRMS_900">{{cite WoRMS |id=900 |title=Terebellida |date=2010-03-03 |last1=Read |first1=Geoffrey |last2=Fauchald |first2=K. |authorlink2=克里斯蒂安·法乌查尔德 |accessdate=2016-03-17 }}</ref><ref name=c&p>{{cite journal |last1=Rouse |first1=G.W. |last2=Fauchald |first2=Kristian |authorlink2=克里斯蒂安·法乌查尔德 |year=1997 |title=Cladistics and polychaetes. |journal=Zoologica Scripta |volume=26|issue=2 |url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1111/j.1463-6409.1997.tb00412.x|doi=10.1111/j.1463-6409.1997.tb00412.x |page=162 |language=en }}</ref>。
根據[[WoRMS|WoRMS]]，本目與[[纓鰓蟲目|纓鰓蟲目]]（[[Sabellida|Sabellida]]）、[[海稚虫目|海稚虫目]]（[[Spionida|Spionida]]）連同一些[[地位未定|地位未定]]的科、屬（例如：[[囊鬚蟲科|囊鬚蟲科]]，泛稱[[原始環蟲類|原始環蟲類]]）共同組成[[管觸鬚下綱|管觸鬚下綱]]<ref name="WoRMS_154974">{{cite WoRMS |id=154974 |title=Canalipalpata |date=2014-02-18 |last=Read |first=Geoffrey |accessdate=2016-03-05 }}</ref><ref name=c&p /><ref name=Rouse1998/> 。這三個目原來都是管觸鬚目未被升格為管觸鬚下綱時之下的三個亞目，是這個分類元的三個主要分支；而管觸鬚下綱同時亦是多毛綱之下的三大分支之一<ref name=Rouse1998>{{cite journal|vauthors=Rouse GW, Fauchald K |title=Recent views on the status, delineation, and classification of the Annelida|journal=[[American_Zoologist|American Zoologist]]|volume=38|issue=6|pages=953–64 |year=1998|doi=10.1093/icb/38.6.953|url=http://icb.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/reprint/38/6/953.pdf|accessdate=2010-11-25|language=en}}</ref>。有其他作者把管觸鬚下綱列為[[亞綱|亞綱]]級<ref name=Rouse1998/>。跟大多數其他多毛綱物種一樣，本目幾乎所有物種皆在海洋生活。
跟其他[[管觸鬚下綱|管觸鬚下綱]]的物種一樣，本科物種均沒有牙或下顎<ref>{{cite book|title=Invertebrate Zoology|first=Robert D. |last=Barnes|year=1980 |edition=4th |isbn=4-8337-0001-8|publisher=Holt-Saunders}}</ref>​。

==系統分類==
蛰龙介目現時有13個科。這13個科尚可以分成[[Cirratuliformia|Cirratuliformia]]和[[Terebellomorpha|Terebellomorpha]]兩個亞目<ref name="WoRMS_900" /><ref name=c&p />，分別如下：
*[[Cirratuliformia|Cirratuliformia]]
**[[Acrocirridae|Acrocirridae]] <small>Banse, 1969</small>：有時被歸入[[Spionida|Spionida]]亞目
** [[丝鳃虫科|丝鳃虫科]]（[[Cirratulidae|Cirratulidae]] <small>Carus, 1863</small>）：有時被歸入[[Spionida|Spionida]]亞目
** Family [[Chloraemidae|Chloraemidae]] <small>Quatrefages, 1849</small>：[[WoRMS|WoRMS]]認為是[[Flabelligeridae|Flabelligeridae]]的同種異名。
** Family [[Ctenodrilidae|Ctenodrilidae]]：有爭議，有時被歸入獨立的[[Ctenodrilida|Ctenodrilida]]亞目。
** Family [[Fauveliopsidae|Fauveliopsidae]] <small>Hartman, 1971</small>：[[WoRMS|WoRMS]]認為是Flabelligeridae的同種異名。
** Family [[Flabelligeridae|Flabelligeridae]] <small>de Saint-Joseph, 1894</small>，有時被歸入獨自的Flabelligerida亞目。
** Family [[Flotidae|Flotidae]] <small>[[加林娜·尼古拉耶芙娜·布仁斯卡婭|Buzhinskaya]], 1996 </small><ref>{{cite journal |last=Buzhinskaya |first=Galina N. |authorlink=加林娜·尼古拉耶芙娜·布仁斯卡婭 |year=1996 |title=Unique morphological features of certain deep-water pelagic polychaetes |journal={{link-ru|Doklady Biological Sciences|Доклады Академии наук}} |volume=347 |pages=139-141 |language=en }}</ref><ref name=Buzhinskaja2006>{{cite journal |url=https://www.zin.ru/journals/zsr/content/2006/zr_2006_15_1_Buzhinskaja.pdf |last=Buzhinskaja |first=G.N. |year=2006 |title=On the morphology of the genus ''Flota'' Hartman, 1967 and corroboration of the family status of Flotidae Buzhinskaja, 1996 (Polychaeta) |journal=Zoosystematica Rossica |volume=15 |issue=1 |pages=7-17 |language=en |access-date=2016-08-29 |archive-date=2016-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911055643/https://www.zin.ru/journals/zsr/content/2006/zr_2006_15_1_Buzhinskaja.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>：[[WoRMS|WoRMS]]認為是Flabelligeridae的同種異名<ref name=WoRMS_833051>{{cite WoRMS |id=833051 |title=Flotidae Buzhinskaya, 1996 |access-date=2016-08-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Osborn |first1=Karen |last2=Rouse |first2=Greg |year=2008 |title=Multiple origins of pelagicism within Flabelligeridae (Annelida). Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution |volume=49 |issue=1 |pages=386-392 |url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.ympev.2008.05.042 |doi=10.1016/j.ympev.2008.05.042 |language=en }}</ref>。
** Family [[Poeobiidae|Poeobiidae]] <small>Heath, 1930</small>：[[WoRMS|WoRMS]]認為也是Flabelligeridae的同種異名<ref name=WoRMS_155083>{{cite WoRMS |id=155083 |title=Poeobiidae Heath, 1930 |access-date=2016-08-29 }}</ref>，亦有其他文獻放在獨自的亞目裡<ref name=Buzhinskaja2006 />。
** [[不倒翁蟲科|不倒翁蟲科]]（[[Sternaspidae|Sternaspidae]] <small>Carus, 1863</small>，有時被歸入[[Sternaspida|Sternaspida]]亞目）
*[[Terebellomorpha|Terebellomorpha]]
** Family [[Alvinellidae|Alvinellidae]]
** Family [[Ampharetidae|Ampharetidae]]<ref>{{cite journal |first=Lars |last=Orrhage |title=On the anatomy of the central nervous system and the morphological value of the anterior end appendages of Ampharetidae, Pectinariidae and Terebellidae (Polychaeta) |year=2001 |journal=Acta Zoologica |volume=82 |issue=1 |pages=57–71 |doi=10.1046/j.1463-6395.2001.00070.x }}</ref>
*** [[Ampharetinae|Ampharetinae]] (ampharetines, a subfamily)
** Family [[Pectinariidae|Pectinariidae]]
** [[蟄龍介科|蟄龍介科]]（[[Terebellidae|Terebellidae]]）
** Family [[Trichobranchidae|Trichobranchidae]]

基於Struck TH在2007-2008年的研究，丝鳃亚目其實可能比其他蛰龙介目物種更為接近[[纓鰓蟲目|纓鰓蟲目]]（[[Sabellida|Sabellida]]）及[[海稚虫目|海稚虫目]]（[[Spionida|Spionida]]）<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Struck |first1=Torsten H. |last2=Schult |first2=Nancy |last3=Kusen |first3=Tiffany |last4=Hickman |first4=E |last5=Bleidorn |first5=C |last6=McHugh |first6=D |last7=Halanych |first7=KM |title=Annelid phylogeny and the status of Sipuncula and Echiura |year=2007 |journal=Bmc Evolutionary Biology |volume=7 |page=57 |PMID=17411434 |doi=10.1186/1471-2148-7-57 |url=http://bmcevolbiol.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1471-2148-7-57 |language=en |accessdate=2016-03-05 |archive-date=2020-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531143823/https://bmcevolbiol.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1471-2148-7-57 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Struck |first1=Torsten H. |last2=Nesnidal |first2=Maximilian P.|last3= Purschke |first3=Günter |last4=Halanych |first4=Keneth M. |title=Detecting possibly saturated positions in 18''S'' and 28''S'' sequences and their influence on phylogenetic reconstruction of Annelida (Lophotrochozoa). |journal=Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution |year=2008 |volume=48 |issue=2 |pages=628–645 |language=en |url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1055790308002522 |doi=10.1016/j.ympev.2008.05.015 }}</ref>。未來這兩個亞目可能會分屬不同的分類支序。

